@startuml seq-federation-stub
' Context: federation
' SDD: SYS-DELIVERY (outbox), bridge-stateless ADR
' Revision: 2026-07-18
' Runtime: stub — dashed = non implementato

title seq-federation-stub — outbox queued → bridge (futuro)

actor Utente
participant "Flutter client" as C
participant "RPC account" as RPC
database "outbox\nprotocol=xmpp|matrix" as OB
participant "bridge-xmpp\n/ bridge-matrix" as B
participant "Server federato" as EXT
database "sync_cursors\nbridge_jobs" as SC

== Outbound (target) ==

Utente -> C : invia a user@server
C -> RPC : send (futuro branch federato)
RPC -> OB : INSERT status=queued\nprotocol=xmpp|matrix
RPC --> C : copia mittente ✓

... outbox resta queued ...

B ..> OB : ClaimOutboxJob\n<<future>>
B ..> EXT : TranslateToExternal\n<<future>>
EXT ..> B : external_id\n<<future>>
B ..> OB : completed + external_id su copia\n<<future>>

== Inbound (target) ==

B ..> SC : PollExternalSync\n<<future>>
EXT ..> B : messaggio / ack\n<<future>>
B ..> RPC : IngestExternalMessage\n+ gate reception\n<<future>>

== Attuale (main) ==

note over B
  GET /health only
  bridge-xmpp :8080
  bridge-matrix :8081
  Nessun claim outbox
end note

C -> C : «Indirizzo esterno\nnon ancora supportato»\n(compose guard)

@enduml
